tagram.com%2Fjustin_yu_1%2F&d=dGuZikqhVjJsCjegsLqG357TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=491b6d77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/justin_yu_1/</a><br />\nTwitter : <a href=\"https://twitter.com/justin_yu_1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjustin_yu_1&d=dGuZikqhVjJsCjegsLqG357TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=883c89d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/justin_yu_1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/FR9gM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FFR9gM.png&h=28783526&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDead by daylight呢隻GAME,係一隻4 VS 1既GAME,4個人類一邊維修發電機一邊避開個殺手,維修夠發電機開大門走佬;玩殺手既就係盡量殺D人,唔俾佢地走到佬<br />\n可惜,呢隻GAME,外國好多人玩,偏偏淨係香港冇人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多係身在外國既香港人,都同我講呢隻GAME外國係勁多人玩,普遍香港人個STEAM都設定係香港,所以香港人買左,馬上開GAME,幾乎係肯定冇場,因為香港SER根本冇人,已經真係有玩開GAME既人,都已經轉哂SER去其他國家玩,而依家最多人既SER而又唔會太LAG既地方,係轉去台灣泰國日本韓國呢D地方既SER玩<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HdDRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHdDRQ.jpg&h=300ec0a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TKEUxPYvRfI?list=PLSow1H3Pe09MwgV9rjsjfYx4FiIKrNU4a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTKEUxPYvRfI%3Flist%3DPLSow1H3Pe09MwgV9rjsjfYx4FiIKrNU4a&d=dGuZikqhVjJsCjegsLqG357TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=0a20940f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TKEUxPYvRfI?list=PLSow1H3Pe09MwgV9rjsjfYx4FiIKrNU4a</a><br />\n由於係香港開CAM開台而又玩呢隻GAME既人,係得我一個台,所以呢隻GAME官方果邊都俾左呢一件twitch台台主先有既SKIN我<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/S1eUb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FS1eUb.jpg&h=8bd1a985&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/S1bmP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FS1bmP.jpg&h=3b0c8436&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/vHoXA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FvHoXA.jpg&h=1fb87b30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下面呢個係隨便台Official LINE群,有咩突發消息,開台通知,我都會係呢度公布<br />\n<img src=\"http://qr-official.line.me/L/aqio2VXZLo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fqr-official.line.me%2FL%2Faqio2VXZLo.png&h=03fd5638&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51880bccf8cafcc5581814dc64b47406af6c56cb","tid":341544,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T01:00:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed81a68421958ea0a9c41f0e0d029670db3385d","tid":341544,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T01:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce7adf3a868877789e1cc47c97cd1498fe43f7a","tid":341544,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T01:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma